summary:
The combination of making people understand each other in the fields of technology, innovation and entrepreneurship has been my passion for the past years. I'm trying to grow my knowledge in this particular field through the relationships with my colleagues, connections and clients.

Currently, I'm focusing on how to make students & professionals grow into self-learning individuals. I'm doing this very thing as a freelance learning designer and Managing Director at Dutch Edtech, which has been a result of my studies, work and network in the Netherlands, Sweden and Australia.

Follow me on Medium -- http://medium.com/@AnnetKloprogge (5.000+ reads)

[{'title': 'Crowdfunding: Isuru Preschool', 'date': {'start': {'month': 4, 'day': None, 'year': 2016}, 'end': {'month': 4, 'day': None, 'year': 2016}}, 'description': 'A short impression of our 2-week working visit to the ISURU Preschool last month together with my team members Mirjam Gelink and Lilian Vos. 

It was a fantastic experience to be with the kids for 2 weeks. We’ve helped the teachers, went on a school trip, celebrated New Years and had the pleasure of attending the school play and New Years games. 

We’ve interviewed parents about the reason to bring their kids to our school and the need for a bigger, more suitable building. We’ve had very efficient meetings with our partner from Sevalanka Foundation, Mr Krishantha and met with the Chairman Mr Harsha Navartane and spend a lot of time with the teachers to find out the plan for next year, their worries, their questions, etc.

The ISURU Preschool is a valuable part of the village of Talpe and needs to continue in a new building that meets all requirements set by the Sri Lankan Educational Ministry. 

We are hopeful and positively optimistic that with support of friends, family, foundations and Stichting Wilde Ganzen we will reach our goal to fund €35.000 to build this new school so ISURU Preschool can stay. 

Wilde Ganzen will add 50% of the total of all funds because they believe in this project!

DONATE:
Stichting Talpe Temple School (ISURU) NL 64 ABNA 0560 114 850

via : Wilde Ganzen: NL53 INGB 00 000 40 000

Betalingskenmerk: 2015.0489 
t.b.v. actieresultaat ‘Uitbreiding en verbetering van de Isuru Pre School’
